# Exclude build artifacts and temporary files
**/.dart_tool/
**/.symlinks/
**/.plugin_symlinks/
**/Flutter/ephemeral/
**/flutter/ephemeral/
**/Build/
**/Builds/
**/*.a
**/*.o
**/*.d
**/*.lib
**/*.dll
**/*.so
**/*.dylib
**/juceaide
**/.DS_Store
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/CMakeFiles/
**/cmake_install.cmake
**/Makefile

# Exclude local agent/workspace docs
AGENTS.md
SKILLS.md

# Exclude local example artifacts
.playwright-mcp/
wajuce-web-*.png
